            <thetext>In the documentation for the qooxdoo mobile NumberField there is described that the NumberField is using the HTML5 input element. In HTML5 the step size for an input is a number, however in qooxdoo the step is an integer. Which means that a step size of 0.1 is not possible in qooxdoo while this is supported on HTML5.</thetext>
